// op_pyin.cpp.jinja — C++ mirror of op_pyin.worklet.js.
// pYIN: Mauch & Dixon 2014, ICASSP. Primary code: github.com/c4dm/pyin (GPL v2+).
// Paper vs code: code wins. Beta tables copied verbatim from YinUtil.cpp L178–L181.
// HMM constants verbatim from MonoPitchHMM.cpp. Our deviations: silent-frame gate,
// fixed-lag online Viterbi (paper silent on online), parabolic refine on d′.

